            "title": "伊朗緊張局勢再起,黃金價格下跌,油價飆升",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pr7WN8CnKJ13X56WaLUKPA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEB7C067_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 週一亞洲交易時段,黃金價格下跌,受到油價反彈的壓力,美伊緊張局勢在本週稍後停火協議到期前幾乎沒有降溫跡象。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">現貨黃金下跌0.6%至每盎司4,802.83美元,而黃金期貨在美國東部時間22:26(格林威治標準時間02:26)下跌1.2%至每盎司4,822.45美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上週,黃金因市場對美伊和平協議的樂觀情緒升溫而錄得溫和漲幅,但這一預期在伊朗於週末再次封鎖霍爾木茲海峽後基本破滅。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-9c1a722a-ffc5-3fb1-ad36-b93244deeba4-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">總統唐納德·川普週日晚間表示,美國向一艘試圖繞過封鎖的伊朗船隻開火並將其捕獲,雙方還聲稱對方違反了停火協議。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普表示,美國特使正前往巴基斯坦進行更多停火談判。但伊朗媒體報導稱,德黑蘭尚未承諾參加任何未來談判。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週一油價飆升高達7%,使市場對伊朗戰爭的通脹影響保持高度警惕。自2月底衝突爆發以來,對能源推動通脹的擔憂一直是金屬價格的主要壓力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在其他貴金屬方面,現貨白銀下跌0.5%至每盎司80.460美元,而現貨鉑金持穩於每盎司2,106.35美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上週白銀表現遠超黃金,此前一份行業報告指出2026年供應短缺將惡化。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E7%B7%8A%E5%BC%B5%E5%B1%80%E5%8B%A2%E5%86%8D%E8%B5%B7-%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C-%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%87-034129291.html",
