            "title": "國際｜伊朗拒絕參加與美國的第二輪談判",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"國際｜伊朗拒絕參加與美國的第二輪談判\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">國際｜伊朗拒絕參加與美國的第二輪談判</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗表示拒絕參加與美國的第二輪談判。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗伊斯蘭共和國通訊社否認伊美雙方將在巴基斯坦談判，指談判前景不明。報道批評美方發放第二輪談判的消息，只是為了施壓伊朗。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報道說，美方提出過分要求，而且不斷改變立場，又持續對伊朗實施海上封鎖、發出威脅言論，這些因素都阻礙談判取得進展。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">較早時，美國總統<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"特朗普\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:特朗普;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/特朗普\">特朗普</a>說，美方代表團將在巴基斯坦首都伊斯蘭堡，與伊朗談判。特朗普說，美國提出的協議公平合理，希望伊朗接受，否則美國將摧毀伊朗所有發電廠和橋樑。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">白宮表示，談判代表團包括副總統萬斯、特朗普特使威特科夫及特朗普的女婿庫什納。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E5%8F%83%E5%8A%A0%E8%88%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E8%BC%AA%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4-030452680.html",
