        {
            "title": "財經｜內地整治「幽靈外賣」助消除及減輕監管不確定性",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜內地整治「幽靈外賣」助消除及減輕監管不確定性\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜內地整治「幽靈外賣」助消除及減輕監管不確定性</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">花旗發表報告，認為國家市場監督管理總局於4月17日宣布對七家電商平台，包括阿里巴巴(09988)、抖音、拼多多、美團(03690)及京東(09618)等因食品安全違規問題處以總額36億元人民幣罰款，此舉合理且可控。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行相信，此事件應被視為正面發展，因為它有助於消除及減輕監管不確定性。有關執法行動亦會促使各平台進一步提升食品安全管控及產品審核能力，有助於為消費者打造一個更安全、更可靠的市場環境，長期而言將增強消費者信任，並促進行業的可持續增長。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%95%B4%E6%B2%BB-%E5%B9%BD%E9%9D%88%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%A3-%E5%8A%A9%E6%B6%88%E9%99%A4%E5%8F%8A%E6%B8%9B%E8%BC%95%E7%9B%A3%E7%AE%A1%E4%B8%8D%E7%A2%BA%E5%AE%9A%E6%80%A7-032937166.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-20 11:40:09",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國4月連續第11個月維持貸款市場報價利率不變",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/64M9sATm19uqdzdtp4hFYw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA7B05U_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 中國4月連續第11個月維持基準貸款利率不變,符合市場預期,顯示在經濟狀況改善的背景下,政策傾向保持穩定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國人民銀行週一公佈的數據顯示,一年期貸款市場報價利率(LPR)維持在3.00%,而作為房貸參考的五年期LPR則維持在3.50%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一決定出爐之際,近期數據顯示全球第二大經濟體展現韌性,第一季度經濟增長加速至約5%,降低了大規模貨幣寬鬆的迫切性。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師表示,隨著通脹顯現企穩跡象且外部風險持續存在,央行可能更傾向依賴定向政策工具,如流動性注入或存款準備金率調整,而非全面降息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B4%E6%9C%88%E9%80%A3%E7%BA%8C%E7%AC%AC11%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E7%B6%AD%E6%8C%81%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E5%A0%B1%E5%83%B9%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%8A-022553851.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-20 10:47:07",
