        {
            "title": "澳洲NEXTDC因數據中心需求激增擬籌資22億澳元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GtKneRkHTHKMYgJTDfJwvg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/asian_2_M_1440047814.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 澳洲NEXTDC Ltd (ASX:NXT)週一表示,隨著數據中心容量需求激增推動合約使用率大幅增長,該公司計劃籌集約22億澳元資金。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司在交易所公告中表示,將進行15億澳元的全額包銷按比例加速不可放棄配股,同時擴大混合證券發行規模至17億澳元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">加拿大投資者La Caisse承諾向混合證券發行額外投入7億澳元,使其總投資額達到17億澳元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">NEXTDC報告稱,截至3月31日,其備考合約使用率躍升250兆瓦至667兆瓦,較12月增長60%,而其遠期訂單量增長83%至544兆瓦,反映出超大規模和人工智能客戶的強勁需求。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b7e615c7-381c-3279-a7b3-f78c62ecbcd3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">新股發行價為每股12.70澳元,較理論除權價格折讓8.6%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">NEXTDC表示,籌集資金將用於加速開發其位於悉尼西部的S4設施,2026財年的資本支出指引上調至最高30億澳元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司預計,現有容量的合約收益最終將超過10億澳元,凸顯出強勁的長期增長前景。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2nextdc%E5%9B%A0%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E6%BF%80%E5%A2%9E%E6%93%AC%E7%B1%8C%E8%B3%8722%E5%84%84%E6%BE%B3%E5%85%83-021148243.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-20 10:47:08",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "財律指揮｜食兩家巨頭茶禮 走入AI圈核心  Marvell仍有上升空間 ｜曲鳴",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"960\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/g6dbvKocwntS91uESZz_bQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/8262ccbf5f2a74f9fca79118e0283700\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美伊和談反反覆覆，與其估談判進展，不如回歸基本步，物色合適的股票去投資AI發展的大趨勢。在AI發展浪潮中，除了直接買科網巨頭，買入得到科網巨頭青睞的公司亦相當不錯，皆因前者會做足DD，證明技術水平值得合作。<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Marvell\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Marvell;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Marvell\">Marvell</a>主打數據基建的半導體解決方案，近日接連得到英偉達20億美元戰略合作協議，又與Google商討TPU上的合作，證明其潛力相當不錯。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">目前Marvell ASIC業務約15億美元，但與谷歌的合作便有高達20億美元的金額，無獨有偶，英偉達戰略投資了20億美元到Marvell，讓後者有足夠的現金拓展AI業務。實際上，以上兩間並非唯一與Marvell有關係的科網巨頭，Marvell與Amazon及微軟都有合作。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4e2580bd-ae33-38a7-b0a8-0f0f9b4cfa5d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雖然Marvell市值未算大，估值未必如一線巨頭般享有極高溢價，但在巨頭們的技術肯定、真金白銀支持下，Marvell 正由「組件供應商」轉型為「AI 基礎設施核心夥伴」。對於追求 AI 長線增長、又不想過度集中於單一顯卡龍頭的投資者而言，這類在科網巨頭處處逢源的半導體企業，不失為當前波動市中更具爆發力的選擇。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">公司股價若回至140美元附近的水平可以考慮買入，中線目標先博200元，若回至120元可加多一注。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%A1%E5%BE%8B%E6%8C%87%E6%8F%AE-%E9%A3%9F%E5%85%A9%E5%AE%B6%E5%B7%A8%E9%A0%AD%E8%8C%B6%E7%A6%AE-%E8%B5%B0%E5%85%A5ai%E5%9C%88%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83-marvell%E4%BB%8D%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87%E7%A9%BA%E9%96%93-%E6%9B%B2%E9%B3%B4-020000767.html",
